        "subject": "LU-1033 build: CentOS kernel 2.6.32-220 new config options.",
        "message": "LU-1033 build: CentOS kernel 2.6.32-220 new config options.\n\nNew kernel options were introduced with the 2.6.32-220 kernel.\nThis patch sets these new options to their default values in\nthe config file.\n\nThis new config file means the Lustre can be built manually (without\nlbuild) and does not require user intevention during the\n'make oldconfig || make menuconfig' phase.\n\nSigned-off-by: Richard Henwood <rhenwood@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I467dec66e6b88ce271a1e7c49452b09878edf26c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
